This R package contains Rust code which depends on the Rust crates listed below.
The source code is vendored in the R package and can also be found at
https://crates.io/crates/XXXX, where XXXX is a crate name.
The authors of these Rust crates are listed below.

Alex Crichton <alex@alexcrichton.com>     : cfg-if, proc-macro2
Andre Bogus <bogusandre@gmail.com>        : typenum
Andreas Longva                            : nalgebra-macros
bluss                                     : either, matrixmultiply, rawpointer
Brendan Zabarauskas <bjzaba@yahoo.com.au> : approx
David B. Dahl <dahl@stat.byu.edu>         : dahl-bellnumber, dahl-partition, dahl-randompartition, dahl-salso, rbindings, roxido, roxido_macro
David Tolnay <dtolnay@gmail.com>          : paste, proc-macro2, quote, syn, unicode-ident
Jack Wrenn <jswrenn@amazon.com>           : zerocopy, zerocopy-derive
Jim Turner                                : ndarray
Jorge Aparicio <jorge@japaric.io>         : libm
Josh Stone <cuviper@gmail.com>            : autocfg, rayon, rayon-core
Joshua Liebow-Feeser <joshlf@google.com>  : zerocopy, zerocopy-derive
Lokathor <zefria@gmail.com>               : bytemuck, safe_arch, wide
Michael Ma                                : statrs
